---
---

<section id="services" class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Services</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
        Comment je peux vous aider
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
        Tout commence par une discussion et un audit gratuit. Ensuite, on voit comment
        travailler ensemble — je m'adapte à votre façon de fonctionner.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <!-- Card 1: Missions ponctuelles -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all group">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-100 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Missions ponctuelles</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Audit d'infrastructure, migration, containerisation, CI/CD, automatisation,
          optimisation des coûts cloud... Je commence toujours par comprendre le vrai
          problème avant de proposer une solution.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
            Linux &amp; Docker
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
            AWS · GCP · Scaleway · OVH
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
            Kubernetes · Ansible · Terraform
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
            GitHub Actions · GitLab CI
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">700 €<span class="text-base font-normal text-gray-400">/jour</span></p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-0.5">Facturation à l'heure possible</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-600 font-medium mt-1">Audit initial gratuit</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Contrats de maintenance -->
      <div class="bg-blue-600 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-blue-600 shadow-lg shadow-blue-100 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500 text-blue-100">Le plus demandé</span>
        </div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m-2-4h.01M17 16h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Contrats de maintenance</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Pour les PME qui ont besoin d'un sysadmin/DevOps sans l'embaucher à temps plein.
          MCO, astreinte, support, sauvegardes — de quoi vous permettre de dormir sur vos deux oreilles.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-blue-100 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-300 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
            Maintien en conditions opérationnelles
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-300 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
            Astreinte &amp; support réactif
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-300 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
            Sauvegardes &amp; monitoring
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-300 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
            1h de gestion mensuelle incluse
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="border-t border-blue-500 pt-6">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">150 € → 3 000 €<span class="text-base font-normal text-blue-200">/mois</span></p>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-200 mt-1">Selon la taille de l'infrastructure</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Urgence -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-red-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all group">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-red-100 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Urgence &amp; Récupération</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Serveur down, site inaccessible, hack WordPress, crash de base de données...
          Un appel, et on s'attaque au problème ensemble. Maintenant.
          Si ce n'est pas dans mes cordes, je connais sans doute quelqu'un qui peut aider.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
            Serveur dédié inaccessible
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
            Crash ou corruption de données
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
            Hack / compromission WordPress
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
            Perte d'accès à une infra
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
          <a
            href="tel:+33649980151"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 w-full justify-center px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-600 text-white font-semibold text-sm transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            +33 6 49 98 01 51
          </a>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 text-center mt-2">Appel direct — selon disponibilité</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
